rows.label: tlk42420151_04_msg0001
rows.name: Do you know about the Harbingers of Eschapon?

rows.label: tlk42420151_04_msg0002
rows.name: Chorrul was deeply moved by them.

rows.label: tlk42420151_04_msg0003
rows.name:
That is the way of thinking necessary
for the future of the Nopon!

rows.label: tlk42420151_04_msg0006
rows.name:
I thought an era was coming where even
Nopon like Chorrul, who aren't good at
the Nopon language, could thrive...
